channel.title: Proxy problems
channel.description:
i did a search for it, nothing good came up, so what im asking is the following:
i have 2 pc's, i play rs on my main on my desktop, and i run aryan on my laptop, but! i dont want to get ip banned, so, how do i setup a proxy so jagex doesn't see my main, i tried that internet explorer stuff, then i went to showmyip.com and it worked, so i logged into rs with my autoer and it said last logged in from *my ip addy*, so that isn't working, isn't there an option to add a proxy to aryan so i can continue autoing?
